---
description: Test directory structure mirrors component structure
globs: installer/tests/**/*
alwaysApply: true
---

The directory structure under `installer/tests/components` must mirror the structure under `installer/src/components`.

For example:
- `installer/src/components/atoms/Headline.tsx` → `installer/tests/components/atoms/Headline.test.tsx`
- `installer/src/components/forms/TextInput.tsx` → `installer/tests/components/forms/TextInput.test.tsx`
- `installer/src/components/molecules/steps/Steps.tsx` → `installer/tests/components/molecules/steps/Steps.test.tsx`
- `installer/src/components/organisms/Header.tsx` → `installer/tests/components/organisms/Header.test.tsx`

When creating new component tests, place them in the corresponding directory structure under `installer/tests/components/` that matches their location under `installer/src/components/`.
